tip.text: One of the best stir fry noodles on This island. If you're Asian & with cravings so try to whip up your own concoction with teriyaki and Sri racha sauce.Pleased to pay €7 for my bowl of udon noodles!!
Suites are nice and decent. Least it's not all the way down which gets tricky when you walk up and down to after a day of visits.  Breakfast to be improve but they are generous with its portions.

tip.text: Pancake is hard as leather! There's flea flying here and there?!!! It's a pity.
Finally I found my favorite green tea with ginseng here!! Must try their home made hummingbird cake. It's to die for!!
Must try their - slow cooked pulled pork sandwich!
Do try their fried beef udon is absolute divine. Friendly staff and great service tho their pricing is bit expensive.
